## 4Ô∏è‚É£ Next.js Project Initialization

```bash
npx create-next-app@latest nextn --typescript
cd nextn
npm install
npx tailwindcss init -p
npx shadcn-ui init
npm install next-pwa lucide-react next-auth mongoose dotenv
```

* Set up App Router (`app/`) and pages
* Integrate Firebase or backend services if needed

---

## 5Ô∏è‚É£ Component Migration & Refactoring

* Copy components to `components/`
* Refactor with Claude for semantic structure, hook adjustments, PWA readiness
* Use VS Code + Copilot for micro-level adjustments
* Log changes in NotebookLM and Explore

---

## 6Ô∏è‚É£ Page Routing & Integration

* Map components to routes (`/dashboard`, `/calendar`, `/journal`)
* Configure dynamic routing for tasks
* Set up global layout & nested layouts
* Validate routing with ChatGPT and Amp Subagents

---

## 7Ô∏è‚É£ State Management & Forms

* Convert state to React Context or Zustand
* Use React Hook Form for forms
* Refactor forms to Next.js pages
* Test hooks & state transitions via Copilot and Claude

